{"type":"message","id":"148c1d13","parentId":"dc11b853","timestamp":"2026-05-10T06:30:07.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's no whisper API key in memory. Let me think about other options for transcribing the voice message. The audio is 9 seconds, 16kHz mono WAV. I need to transcribe it somehow.\n\nWait - I could use the OpenAI API directly since the MEMORY says primary model is `thaigq/deepseek-v4-pro:cloud` with provider `thaigq`. But that might not support transcription. The OpenAI-compatible API endpoint is at `https://ollama-pay.thaigqsoft.com/api/v1`.\n\nActually, let me check if there's a transcription endpoint available through the same provider. \n\nI'm realizing the MiniMax model doesn't support audio transcription - that's typically a separate model like Whisper. Since I can't install packages and don't have an API key readily available, I need to explore what other tools might work for this 9-second voice message. I'm thinking through other options—maybe a community voice recognition tool or something that doesn't require installation, or perhaps I could try a direct API call to MiniMax's transcription endpoint. But honestly, since I can't really transcribe audio effectively with what I have available, I should just ask the user what they actually said since I can't process voice messages properly.\n","thinkingSignature":"ae150f301ec87f86f2b40acd6ca68d504d8a4d829f4088679b0b93f2d9d5258a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n🧑🏼‍💻 ขออภัยครับเจ้านาย ผมยังไม่มีวิธีถอดเสียง (transcribe) จากไฟล์ OGG ได้ในตอนนี้ เพราะ:\n\n- ไม่มี pip ติดตั้งในระบบ\n- ไม่มี OpenAI API key สำหรับ Whisper API\n- ไม่มีโมเดล transcription บน Ollama\n\n---\n\n**แนวทางแก้ไข:**\n\n1. **ส่ง Whisper API key มาให้** → ผมเชื่อมต่อ OpenAI Whisper API ได้เลย\n2. **ติดตั้ง pip** → `sudo apt install python3-pip` (ต้องใส่ password)\n3. **เปลี่ยนเป็นพิมพ์ข้อความแทน** → เจ้านายพิมพ์เองเร็วกว่าครับ 😄\n\nจะให้ผมดำเนินการอย่างไรครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2583,"output":587,"cacheRead":30720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33890,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778394587477,"responseId":"064f58dca2596f53d2de3d9568a8c3b8"}}
