{"type":"message","id":"d081c22e","parentId":"de04e908","timestamp":"2026-05-10T06:43:57.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the scripts - one for loading Whisper into RAM (enable) and one for unloading it (disable). I'll also create a Python module that keeps the model in memory.\n\nLet me create:\n1. `scripts/_whisper_manager.py` - module that handles model loading/unloading with state\n2. `scripts/enable_whisper.py` - /เปิดเสียงพูด command\n3. `scripts/disable_whisper.py` - /ปิดเสียงพูด command\n\nThen I'll write the SKILL.md.\n\nFor the commands - the user wants them as skill commands. Looking at MEMORY.md, commands are configured with `commands.native` and `commands.text`. The boss uses `/เปิดเสียงพูด` etc. \n\nSo these need to be registered as native commands in the OpenClaw config. I'll create the SKILL.md with instructions for how to register these commands, and then write the scripts for enabling and disabling the Whisper model.\n","thinkingSignature":"cd51d64efb794481042325e1b345f8d5ff07132ad3aba89e634e5535677b58b8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nตอนนี้ Whisper รองรับแล้ว (large-v3-turbo 1.5GB อยู่ใน RAM) 🧑🏼‍💻 กำลังสร้าง skill ครับ...\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pzuctzkbcy43_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nWhisper model manager - keeps model loaded in RAM for fast transcription.\nState: single global model instance held in this module.\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\n\n_MODEL_PATH = \"/home/apinan/.cache/whisper/large-v3-turbo.pt\"\n_STATE_FILE = \"/tmp/whisper_model_state.txt\"\n\n_model = None\n_model_info = None\n\ndef is_loaded():\n    \"\"\"Check if model is currently in RAM.\"\"\"\n    global _model\n    return _model is not None\n\ndef load():\n    \"\"\"Load Whisper model into RAM (int8 CPU). Returns (ok, message).\"\"\"\n    global _model, _model_info\n    if _model is not None:\n        return True, \"Whisper model already loaded in RAM (1.51 GB)\"\n\n    try:\n        from faster_whisper import WhisperModel\n        print(\"Loading Whisper large-v3-turbo into RAM...\", file=sys.stderr)\n        _model = WhisperModel(\"large-v3-turbo\", device=\"cpu\", compute_type=\"int8\")\n        _model_info = {\n            \"size_gb\": os.path.getsize(_MODEL_PATH) / (1024**3),\n            \"compute\": \"int8\",\n            \"device\": \"cpu\"\n        }\n        # Persist state\n        with open(_STATE_FILE, \"w\") as f:\n            f.write(\"loaded\")\n        return True, f\"Whisper model loaded into RAM ({_model_info['size_gb']:.2f} GB, int8 CPU)\"\n    except Exception as e:\n        return False, f\"Failed to load Whisper: {e}\"\n\ndef unload():\n    \"\"\"Unload Whisper model from RAM. Returns (ok, message).\"\"\"\n    global _model, _model_info\n    if _model is None:\n        return True, \"Whisper model already unloaded\"\n\n    try:\n        del _model\n        _model = None\n        _model_info = None\n        if os.path.exists(_STATE_FILE):\n            os.remove(_STATE_FILE)\n        # Suggest garbage collection\n        import gc\n        gc.collect()\n        return True, \"Whisper model unloaded from RAM\"\n    except Exception as e:\n        return False, f\"Failed to unload: {e}\"\n\ndef transcribe(wav_path):\n    \"\"\"Transcribe a WAV file. Returns (text, info) or raises.\"\"\"\n    if _model is None:\n        raise RuntimeError(\"Whisper model not loaded. Run /เปิดเสียงพูด first.\")\n    segments, info = _model.transcribe(wav_path, beam_size=5, language=\"th\")\n    text = \"\".join(s.text for s in segments)\n    return text, info\n\ndef get_status():\n    \"\"\"Return current model status.\"\"\"\n    if _model is None:\n        return {\"loaded\": False, \"size_gb\": None}\n    return {\n        \"loaded\": True,\n        \"size_gb\": os.path.getsize(_MODEL_PATH) / (1024**3),\n        \"compute\": \"int8\",\n        \"device\": \"cpu\"\n    }\n\n# Auto-load on import if state file exists\nif os.path.exists(_STATE_FILE):\n    load()","path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/scripts/_whisper_manager.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":245,"output":1010,"cacheRead":40832,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778395409478,"responseId":"064f5c12c961c07763a17afc7f2bde5c"}}
