{"type":"message","id":"9e80012e","parentId":"b97ad482","timestamp":"2026-05-10T06:44:30.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write the SKILL.md for the voice-speech skill.\n","thinkingSignature":"a99584856a50eff49908bef331212763b88652b0ebc130ca4b84cbe6f5c605f6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bi3t9sng8dtc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: voice-speech\ndescription: \"Transcribe Thai voice messages using Whisper (faster-whisper + large-v3-turbo model loaded in RAM). Triggers when: user sends a voice/audio message, user asks to transcribe audio, user says /เปิดเสียงพูด or /ปิดเสียงพูด, or any request related to voice-to-text, transcription, or speech recognition. Model (~1.5 GB) lives in RAM after /เปิดเสียงพูด so transcription is fast. WAV file should be 16kHz mono PCM (auto-converted from OGG via ffmpeg).\"\n---\n\n# Voice Speech Skill\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Step 1: Convert OGG → WAV (ffmpeg)\n\n```bash\nffmpeg -i <input.ogg> -ar 16000 -ac 1 -c:a pcm_s16le <output.wav> -y\n```\n\n### Step 2: Transcribe\n\n```bash\npython3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/scripts')\nfrom _whisper_manager import transcribe\ntext, info = transcribe('/path/to/file.wav')\nprint(text)\nprint(f'Language: {info.language} ({info.language_probability:.2f})')\n\"\n```\n\n## Commands\n\n### `/เปิดเสียงพูด` — Load Whisper into RAM\n\nRun once at session start or on first voice message:\n\n```bash\npython3 /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/scripts/load_whisper.py\n```\n\nCheck status:\n\n```bash\npython3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/scripts')\nfrom _whisper_manager import get_status\nprint(get_status())\n\"\n```\n\n### `/ปิดเสียงพูด` — Unload Whisper from RAM\n\nFree ~1.5 GB RAM when done:\n\n```bash\npython3 /home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/scripts/unload_whisper.py\n```\n\n## State Management\n\n- `is_loaded()` — Check if model in RAM\n- `load()` — Load model (int8 CPU, ~1.5 GB)\n- `unload()` — Unload and gc.collect()\n- State persisted in `/tmp/whisper_model_state.txt` (auto-reload on module import)\n\n## Model Details\n\n- Model: `large-v3-turbo` (Whisper)\n- Location: `/home/apinan/.cache/whisper/large-v3-turbo.pt` (1.51 GB)\n- Compute: int8 CPU\n- Language: Thai (forced with `language=\"th\"`)\n- Beam size: 5\n\n## Requirements (auto-installed)\n\n```\nfaster-whisper>=1.2.0\nffmpeg (system)\n```\n\nRequired Python packages are already installed. If not present: `pip install faster-whisper`.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Model loads in ~10-30s first time, then stays hot in RAM\n- Transcription takes ~3-8s for a 10s voice clip\n- WAV must be 16kHz mono PCM — ffmpeg handles conversion automatically\n- If model not loaded when transcription requested, auto-load first","path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/plugin-skills/voice-speech/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":175,"output":781,"cacheRead":41984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778395447143,"responseId":"064f5c3850a169dc9c10b505f3180cf8"}}
