{"type":"message","id":"86193d84","parentId":"34c1b035","timestamp":"2026-05-10T07:03:56.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The transcription process keeps getting killed with SIGKILL after 20-30 seconds of the actual transcription. This suggests the OOM killer is terminating the process. The model is loaded (1.5GB) and the audio file is being processed - during beam search the memory usage probably spikes.\n\nLet me try a completely different approach - use the Ollama transcription model. I don't have a transcription model in Ollama, but let me check if there's one available.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The issue is that:\n1. Model is loaded in RAM: ~1.5GB\n2. Transcription process starts\n3. Memory usage spikes during beam search computation\n\n\n4. System runs out of memory (MemAvailable = 18GB, should be enough... but maybe it's the WSL2 memory limit)\n5. OOM killer sends SIGKILL\n\nI should try switching to a lighter model like `base` or `small` instead of `large-v3-turbo` to reduce memory pressure during transcription.\n\nActually, let me reconsider - the large-v3-turbo model is 1.5GB and I have 18GB available, so the issue might be in the computation itself rather than just loading the model. When faster-whisper runs beam search with `beam_size=5`, it could be creating additional tensors that spike memory usage. I should try reducing the beam size to see if that helps.\n\nBut wait, SIGKILL with exit code 124 from `timeout` suggests the timeout command itself is terminating the process, not necessarily the OOM killer - though the process was definitely running for over 30 seconds. Let me try reducing beam_size to 1 and using only 2 threads to see if that prevents the crash.\n","thinkingSignature":"9a39260014afbad0355c54bc574529657feb104b2480f22696dd7c365dee3503"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mqdxx6tbyr4n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test with minimal resources\nffmpeg -i /home/apinan/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_44---0a7e6c51-e1a1-46e3-a23f-d1573e1c9893.ogg -ar 16000 -ac 1 -c:a pcm_s16le /tmp/v44c.wav -y 2>/dev/null\ntimeout 60 python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sys, os\nfrom faster_whisper import WhisperModel\n\n# Reload with minimal memory footprint\nmodel = WhisperModel(\"large-v3-turbo\", device=\"cpu\", compute_type=\"int8\", num_workers=1)\nsegments, info = model.transcribe(\"/tmp/v44c.wav\", beam_size=1, language=\"th\", vad_filter=True)\ntext = \"\".join(s.text for s in segments)\nprint(text.strip())\nos.unlink(\"/tmp/v44c.wav\")\nEOF","timeout":70,"yieldMs":50000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":138,"output":599,"cacheRead":53120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53857,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778396609421,"responseId":"064f60c37abc2d332794ed93fa960ba7"}}
