{"type":"message","id":"d5d7a56a","parentId":"688dea59","timestamp":"2026-05-10T07:58:41.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found several Thai TTS options. Let me search for more specific information about F5-TTS Thai and MMS-TTS Thai, as well as looking into whether I can use Google's TTS directly via their API without paying.\n\nThe key options I found:\n1. **MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE** - Open-source, fine-tuned Thai male TTS from Play.ht data\n2. **VIZINTZOR/F5-TTS-THAI** - On Hugging Face\n3. **PyThaiNLP/PyThaiTTS** - Open source Thai TTS library\n4. **Typhoon-TTS** - Thai voice research from.opentyphoon.ai\n\n\n5. **Kokoro/Piper/MeloTTS** - open source options that support Thai\n\nI should focus on the most promising ones to download and test, particularly MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE and F5-TTS-THAI, while also checking if Google's TTS API offers a free tier I can leverage.\n","thinkingSignature":"7c5535d8ec883aa1ac7d65832efaf71b1f9b5922885016c1a9fd1de0402f7c17"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zkntsm208zzb_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"F5-TTS Thai model Hugging Face install usage Kokoro TTS Thai voice"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1928,"output":263,"cacheRead":76288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78479,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778399907805,"responseId":"064f6da5707169779d606b58da14a054"}}
