arch\\n---\\nf5-tts · PyPI\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"75fe69c302cdf30c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://pypi.org/project/f5-tts/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4ba2cc8d5b1fbbf6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nF5-TTS : A Fairytaler that Fakes Fluent and Faithful Speech with Flow Matching F5-TTS : Diffusion Transformer with ConvNeXt V2, faster trained and inference. E2 TTS : Flat-UNet Transformer, closest reproduction from paper. Sway Sampling: Inference-time flow step sampling strategy, greatly improves performance Thanks to all the contributors ! News 2025/03/12: 🔥 F5-TTS v1 base model with better ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4ba2cc8d5b1fbbf6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"pypi.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"81c673695aea4712\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nF5-TTS-THAI: Text-to-Audio model — overview, use cases, alternatives\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"81c673695aea4712\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.aimodels.fyi/models/huggingFace/f5-tts-thai-vizintzor\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"506beb1a992e28e9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOverview F5 - TTS - THAI is a Thai language text-to-speech model built on the F5-TTS architecture, trained to 1,000,000 steps on approximately 500 hours of audio data. Developed by VIZINTZOR, the model supports both Thai and English languages and performs voice cloning by taking a reference audio sample (2-8 seconds recommended) and reference text to generate new speech with matching voice ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"506beb1a992e28e9\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.aimodels.fyi\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0969104a41719f08\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\ntts_kokoro.ipynb - Colab\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0969104a41719f08\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://colab.research.google.com/github/YuxiaoLuo/AI_Intro/blob/main/tts/tts_kokoro.ipynb\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf3e5c8f33fc4474\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThis tutorial introudces the #1 TTS model (as of Jan 15 2025) in the Hugging Face TTS Arena Leaderboard, Kokoro-TTS . The magic about this model is it's very small-size (only 82 million, trained on < 100 hours of audio), but its performance is very good.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf3e5c8f33fc4474\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"colab.research.google.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"F5-TTS Thai model Hugging Face install usage Kokoro TTS Thai voice","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":999,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73c2c092e0d26c40\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nVIZINTZOR/F5-TTS-THAI · Hugging Face\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"73c2c092e0d26c40\">>>","url":"https://huggingface.co/VIZINTZOR/F5-TTS-THAI","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf85671cdd67c462\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWe're on a journey to advance and democratize artificial intelligence through open source and open science.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf85671cdd67c462\">>>","siteName":"huggingface.co"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7427bc6dd2b2dfde\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nVYNCX/F5-TTS-THAI - GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7427bc6dd2b2dfde\">>>","url":"https://github.com/VYNCX/F5-TTS-THAI","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b90e0a577baa6be0\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nF5-TTS : A Fairytaler that Fakes Fluent and Faithful Speech with Flow Matching. Support For Thai language. Text-to-Speech ( TTS ) ภาษาไทย — เครื่องมือสร้างเสียงพูดจากข้อความด้วยเทคนิค Flow Matching ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b90e0a577baa6be0\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"75fe69c302cdf30c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nf5-tts · PyPI\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"75fe69c302cdf30c\">>>","url":"https://pypi.org/project/f5-tts/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4ba2cc8d5b1fbbf6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nF5-TTS : A Fairytaler that Fakes Fluent and Faithful Speech with Flow Matching F5-TTS : Diffusion Transformer with ConvNeXt V2, faster trained and inference. E2 TTS : Flat-UNet Transformer, closest reproduction from paper. Sway Sampling: Inference-time flow step sampling strategy, greatly improves performance Thanks to all the contributors ! News 2025/03/12: 🔥 F5-TTS v1 base model with better ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4ba2cc8d5b1fbbf6\">>>","siteName":"pypi.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"81c673695aea4712\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nF5-TTS-THAI: Text-to-Audio model — overview, use cases, alternatives\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"81c673695aea4712\">>>","url":"https://www.aimodels.fyi/models/huggingFace/f5-tts-thai-vizintzor","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"506beb1a992e28e9\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOverview F5 - TTS - THAI is a Thai language text-to-speech model built on the F5-TTS architecture, trained to 1,000,000 steps on approximately 500 hours of audio data. Developed by VIZINTZOR, the model supports both Thai and English languages and performs voice cloning by taking a reference audio sample (2-8 seconds recommended) and reference text to generate new speech with matching voice ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"506beb1a992e28e9\">>>","siteName":"www.aimodels.fyi"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0969104a41719f08\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\ntts_kokoro.ipynb - Colab\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0969104a41719f08\">>>","url":"https://colab.research.google.com/github/YuxiaoLuo/AI_Intro/blob/main/tts/tts_kokoro.ipynb","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf3e5c8f33fc4474\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThis tutorial introudces the #1 TTS model (as of Jan 15 2025) in the Hugging Face TTS Arena Leaderboard, Kokoro-TTS . The magic about this model is it's very small-size (only 82 million, trained on < 100 hours of audio), but its performance is very good.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf3e5c8f33fc4474\">>>","siteName":"colab.research.google.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778399922507}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d17e762","parentId":"106c2474","timestamp":"2026-05-10T07:58:58.426Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have good info. Let me summarize:\n\n1. **F5-TTS-THAI** - Thai text-to-audio model built on F5-TTS architecture, supports Thai + English, does voice cloning with 2-8s reference audio\n2. **Kokoro-TTS** - #1 on Hugging Face TTS Arena, very small (82M params), good quality, has Thai voices\n3. **MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE** - Open-source Thai male TTS\n4. **PyThaiNLP/PyThaiTTS** - Open source Thai TTS library\n5. **Typhoon-TTS** - Thai voices, from a Thai research group\n\n\n6. **F5-TTS** is available on PyPI and supports voice cloning with reference audio, though it requires GPU for decent performance\n\nThe most practical approach would be trying Kokoro if Thai voices are available through its pipeline, or combining F5-TTS-THAI with a reference audio sample for cloning. MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE offers a simpler offline alternative. Let me dig into what's actually available locally.\n","thinkingSignature":"d7c471684678854edae5b1abd7a878e928b5710a0cad0701e861bd583231cc90"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zdgau7xgvogs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -m pip show kokoro-tts 2>/dev/null; python3 -m pip show TTS 2>/dev/null | head -3; python3 -m pip show coqui-tts 2>/dev/null | head -3; which espeak 2>/dev/null; python3 -c \"import pyttsx3; print('pyttsx3 ok')\" 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1475,"output":346,"cacheRead":78144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79965,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778399922512,"responseId":"064f6db3c6169403c50ae4bf1c75d553"}}
