{"type":"message","id":"b64b73db","parentId":"0817f181","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:06:16.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works! pythaitts with facebook/mms-tts-concat can generate Thai speech. The output is saved to a temp WAV file. Let me clean up and report back to the boss.\n\nBut actually - this is TTS (text-to-speech), not the voice transcription that the boss was initially asking about. The boss originally said the TTS voice quality is not good. Now I've found a local Thai TTS option that works.\n\nLet me summarize the findings for the boss:\n1. Kokoro TTS - no Thai voices (only en, fr, ja, cmn)\n2. Piper - no Thai voice models available\n\n\n3. pythaitts (facebook/mms-tts-concat) - works! Thai male voice, but it's a Conformer model so quality may not be the best\n4. XTTS-v2 - would need Coqui TTS library, heavy\n\nSo the best option right now is pythaitts with facebook/mms-tts-concat for Thai TTS. But wait - the boss actually asked about the model that speaks back (TTS), not the transcription model. Let me reread what they said: \"ไม่ใช่โมเดลถอดเสียงเป็นเทค\" - they were clarifying they're not talking about the transcription model, but rather what model I use to speak back to them.\n\nThey want a male Thai voice that sounds natural, like Google's Gemini. Looking at available options, pythaitts with facebook/mms-tts-concat works but the quality isn't great. I should search for MMS-TTS Thai male variants or other better Thai TTS options instead.\n","thinkingSignature":"3995159ff376aff2b2144ff2de9ea269cafc9746e30b1cf0ea3bd1bcc0f4f26a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2g2s9wcjedu5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom pythaitts import TTS\nt = TTS()\n# List available models\nprint('Pretrained options:', t.pretrained)\n\" 2>&1 | grep -v \"Warning\\|HF Hub\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":322,"output":430,"cacheRead":91584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778400353295,"responseId":"064f6f6388fb0e550de24e1a3d7ffd91"}}
