{"type":"message","id":"e8e37b02","parentId":"ba6b59de","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:11:03.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss wants me to get 3-4 free Thai TTS voices and send audio samples for them to listen to. Let me find some free Thai TTS options and generate samples.\n\nLet me focus on what's actually installable locally without GPU:\n\n1. **Kokoro-TTS** - has no Thai voices natively but maybe I can find Thai voice pack\n2. **Piper Thai** - need to find Thai voice model\n3. **Coqui XTTS v2** - but needs GPU usually\n4. **espeak-ng** - has Thai but sounds robotic\n\n\n5. **OpenAI TTS API** - not free\n\nI'm thinking the most practical path forward is to set up a proper TTS server using Coqui XTTS v2 with CPU support, though it might be slow, or fall back to MMS-TTS for Thai which should work on CPU. I could also explore Bark or other transformer-based TTS options that have Thai support, or just do a web search to find which free Thai TTS voices are actually available and working.\n","thinkingSignature":"c84e17c1b8a86d967d1ca1996ec829fa1072e5141415d1311ffb72b708e878cf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ptmlwcv3hc5i_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":8,"query":"Thai text to speech free male voice ONNX CPU local Windows Linux 2024 download"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":19202,"output":269,"cacheRead":74048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778400647545,"responseId":"064f70890f5da22f9fb2aa046bd20b2b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"492dc11b","parentId":"e8e37b02","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:11:05.185Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ptmlwcv3hc5i_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Thai text to speech free male voice ONNX CPU local Windows Linux 2024 download\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 8,\n  \"tookMs\": 915,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e841a5f74478e776\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - PyThaiNLP/thaitts-onnx: Thai Text-to-speech by ONNX runtime\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e841a5f74478e776\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/PyThaiNLP/thaitts-onnx\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"311ca6953a930009\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nToday, Thai Text-to-speech doesn't have any onnx model for onnxruntime. We use TTS model from lunarlist/tts- thai -last-step but the model is lockout that needs has NeMo (and NeMo doesn't support export Tacotron2 to ONNX model since 2020).\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"311ca6953a930009\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1900e723c24d493d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\npythainlp/thaitts-onnx · Hugging Face\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1900e723c24d493d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://huggingface.co/pythainlp/thaitts-onnx\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d6dbdf4ce625cd0\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWe're on a journey to advance and democratize artificial intelligence through open source and open science.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d6dbdf4ce625cd0\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"huggingface.co\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"876c6fe9bccc9492\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nKokoro Local TTS: Offline Custom Voices\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"876c6fe9bccc9492\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://kokorotts-ai.com/kokoro-tts-local\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e7bd158e4f8e775a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nKokoro 82M is a compact local text-to-speech model that produces high-quality voice output without sending data to external services. Voices are defined by embeddings, which makes customization straightforward. You can run it in a notebook, switch to ONNX for fast local inference, and even expose it as a local API that mirrors a familiar endpoint.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e7bd158e4f8e775a\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"kokorotts-ai.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"608b571821f617f4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTTS - Thai open-source Thai text-to-speech model - Free conversion of ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"608b571821f617f4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://model.aibase.com/en/models/details/1915693302051135489\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"59a76cd1ab6e8eec\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n## 🚀 Thai Text-to-Speech Model *This is a Thai Text-to-Speech (TTS) model that utilizes voices from the Common Voice dataset and modifies them to sound distinct from the original.* ## 🚀 Quick Start To use this model, you first need to install the necessary libraries.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"59a76cd1ab6e8eec\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"model.aibase.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dd083706ddb64c96\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPiper TTS - Easy With AI\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"dd083706ddb64c96\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://easywithai.com/ai-text-to-speech/piper-tts/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d8f02ff6a7ee9488\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPiper is a fast, local text-to-speech system optimized for Linux , and Raspberry Pi (it can also be run on Windows via Python). It features pretrained voices in over 30 languages and can accept text input or JSON to synthesize high-quality audio. Piper is open-source and written in C++ and Python, with binaries available for desktop Linux , Raspberry Pi, and more. You need to provide a onnx ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"d8f02ff6a7ee9488\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"easywithai.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82de5987818fe9d8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThai text to speech - Narakeet\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"82de5987818fe9d8\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.narakeet.com/languages/thai-text-to-speech/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f5a7d67084e78af2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGet started with Thai text to speech free , using realistic AI voice generators. Select from one of our text-to-speech Thai male and female voices below, and enter some text to create the audio.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f5a7d67084e78af2\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.narakeet.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea75762eead1bf1f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFast local TTS inference engine in C# with ONNX runtime. Multi-speaker ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ea75762eead1bf1f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/Lyrcaxis/KokoroSharp\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f4732bb95ce6b8ed\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nKokoroSharp is a fully-featured inference engine for Kokoro TTS, built entirely in C# with ONNX runtime. It enables developers to perform flexible and fast text-to-speech synthesis utilizing multiple speakers and languages.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f4732bb95ce6b8ed\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"05966f01e8865ab5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNeuML/txtai-speecht5-onnx · Hugging Face\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"05966f01e8865ab5\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://huggingface.co/NeuML/txtai-speecht5-onnx\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4836338f525e3625\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWe're on a journey to advance and democratize artificial intelligence through open source and open science.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4836338f525e3625\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"huggingface.co\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Thai text to speech free male voice ONNX CPU local Windows Linux 2024 download","provider":"duckduckgo","count":8,"tookMs":915,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e841a5f74478e776\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGitHub - PyThaiNLP/thaitts-onnx: Thai Text-to-speech by ONNX runtime\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e841a5f74478e776\">>>","url":"https://github.com/PyThaiNLP/thaitts-onnx","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"311ca6953a930009\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nToday, Thai Text-to-speech doesn't have any onnx model for onnxruntime. We use TTS model from lunarlist/tts- thai -last-step but the model is lockout that needs has NeMo (and NeMo doesn't support export Tacotron2 to ONNX model since 2020).\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"311ca6953a930009\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1900e723c24d493d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\npythainlp/thaitts-onnx · Hugging Face\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1900e723c24d493d\">>>","url":"https://huggingface.co/pythainlp/thaitts-