{"type":"message","id":"e3a1ce44","parentId":"e4bc47de","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:24:00.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, I got two gTTS samples. Let me send them both to the boss to try. gTTS is Google's free TTS - it might sound robotic but it's free and Thai works.\n","thinkingSignature":"5c01952e995d0164e59cc16e68629f90c19e73e55fd0fd1f8775e27e0da91908"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nส่งตัวอย่างเสียงให้ฟังครับ\n\nMEDIA:/tmp/tts_gtts.wav\n\n**gTTS (Google Free TTS)** — ภาษาไทย ฟรี แต่เป็นเสียงหญิง\n\n---\n\nMEDIA:/tmp/tts_gtts2.wav\n\n**gTTS (Google Free TTS)** — ตัวอย่างที่ 2\n\n---\n\ngTTS เป็นตัวเลือกฟรีสุด แต่เสียงอาจไม่ natural เท่า TTS ที่จ่ายตัวครับ 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":256,"output":231,"cacheRead":113792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114279,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778401423621,"responseId":"064f7390df30424b9d57b1a100f410c0"}}
