{"type":"message","id":"59dbfcab","parentId":"52aeb788","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:29:47.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The v1 version requires authentication. Let me try to use the existing v0 model with a different approach to make it sound better, or try the edge-tts that's already working. Or maybe I should try the MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-V1 from aibate model page which might have a different download link.\n\nActually, the user is asking if the 5 TTS models I found earlier can be used. Let me try the VITS model from k2-fsa which has Thai support via MeloTTS. Let me also check the free.ai TTS which uses Kokoro and Piper for Thai voices.\n","thinkingSignature":"a10bfd13d844225fd928799a6163e353eceb0ca906a23f21f1c635d5e5c99a07"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bj47g4qhq7ca_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom gtts import gTTS\ntts = gTTS(text='สวัสดีครับ ผมโอเว่น เลขาส่วนตัวของคุณ พร้อมรับใช้ครับ', lang='th')\ntts.save('/tmp/tts_thai_free.wav')\nprint('OK')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22875,"output":262,"cacheRead":92288,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115425,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778401767287,"responseId":"064f74e9835c21f22313955eb1f41bee"}}
