{"type":"message","id":"c0577acd","parentId":"1bdf3cfb","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:30:07.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me just send the current Thai TTS sample and ask if it's acceptable. The current options are limited. Let me also try to see if there's a way to use the VIZINTZOR model with a different approach.\n\nActually, let me check what \"5 Thai TTS\" the user is referring to. Maybe they mean the MMS-TTS Thai Male V1 or the thaitts-onnx model from PyThaiNLP. Let me check the aibase model page for MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-V1.\n","thinkingSignature":"8ad4701afc6fdf13454b62b16c2eb8177616c2a02d008e568326c05ad364d147"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cvs7vjwbdjzg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom transformers import AutoModel, AutoTokenizer, VitsModel\nimport torch, warnings, soundfile as sf\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# Load the first version which we know works\nmodel = AutoModel.from_pretrained('VIZINTZOR/MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-NARRATOR')\ntok = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained('VIZINTZOR/MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-NARRATOR')\n\ntext = 'มึงทำงานได้เร็วขึ้นกว่านี้ได้ไหม ผมอยากให้ถอดเสียงกูได้ไว้'\ninputs = tok(text, return_tensors='pt')\nwith torch.no_grad():\n    output = model(**inputs)\naudio = output.waveform[0].cpu().numpy()\nsf.write('/tmp/tts_mms2.wav', audio, 16000)\nprint('OK, duration:', len(audio)/16000, 'sec')\n\" 2>&1 | grep -v \"Warning\\|HF_HUB\\|huggingface\\|download\\|CUDA\\|LOAD REPORT\\|discriminator\\|UNEXPECTED\\|Notes\\|Key\\|Status\\|can be ignored\"","timeout":60,"yieldMs":50000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":241,"output":430,"cacheRead":115072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115743,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778401787730,"responseId":"064f74fd502f67d96b626586b23af070"}}
