{"type":"message","id":"f35331c6","parentId":"b67f0c8b","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:34:12.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try to download the actual model files from the aibase page or HuggingFace more carefully. Let me also try to search for a Thai male TTS that's actually good quality and free.\n\nActually, the user said \"Thai TTS 5 ตัวที่มึงเคยหา\" - maybe they're referring to the 5 options I listed earlier in the conversation. But the ones I found were:\n1. Kokoro-TTS - no Thai voices\n2. MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-NARRATOR (v1) - works but bad quality\n3. gTTS - works but female voice\n\n\n4. PyThaiTTS - very short audio\n5. F5-TTS-THAI - voice cloning, needs reference audio\n\nI should check if there are other Thai TTS models on HuggingFace that I might have missed, or look into running Piper TTS which might have better Thai voice options available.\n","thinkingSignature":"e306e067b43f8d48c2d514bfc27cf0e2ebc349b3ebd001afa282cd12323ecbd9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lfldn0i39qdl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check what PyThaiNLP thaitts-onnx has\npython3 -c \"\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/apinan/.local/lib/python3.12/site-packages')\nimport thaitts_onnx\nprint(dir(thaitts_onnx))\nhelp(thaitts_onnx)\n\" 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":300,"cacheRead":116672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117241,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778402034052,"responseId":"064f75f3613f682b1010d6e5dcc8e7e2"}}
