{"type":"message","id":"e681b6c1","parentId":"60a2769d","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:35:44.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't have specific memory about \"Thai TTS 5\" that I found before. The boss is asking about Thai TTS that I previously found - maybe referring to the 5 Thai TTS options I searched for earlier in this conversation. Let me re-read the earlier search results.\n\nLooking back at the earlier search results, I found several Thai TTS options:\n1. MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-NARRATOR (VIZINTZOR) - we tried, quality is bad\n2. MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-V1 - tried to load but repo not found\n3. wannaphong/khanomtan-tts-v1.0 - Vits model but couldn't load\n\n\n4. Kokoro TTS - no Thai voices\n5. free.ai Thai TTS - powered by Kokoro, Piper, and MeloTTS\n\nThat's actually 4 Thai TTS options I've found so far, not 5. I should probably be honest with the boss that I don't have 5 Thai TTS options readily available - I've really only found 4 in my searches, with the first one being poor quality and the second having repository access issues.\n\nLet me think about what other Thai TTS systems I might be missing. There's thaitts-onnx from PyThaiNLP, but it doesn't have pretrained models to download. And looking at this aibase result, it seems like a v1 and v2 of MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE that might be better quality than what I've already tested. But the v1 repository isn't accessible anymore, and I don't have any additional Thai TTS options beyond what I've listed.\n","thinkingSignature":"28a639321e3324c96171f6d7f02927c054f192ffc29c3e00829b606d04be37bc"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nขอโทษครับเจ้านาย — ที่หาเจอใน conversation นี้มีแค่ 4 ตัว:\n\n1. **MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-NARRATOR** — เสียงผู้ชาย แต่ห่วย (ที่ส่งไปแล้ว)\n2. **MMS-TTS-THAI-MALE-V1** — repo ไม่เจอ (ต้อง token)\n3. **KhanomTan TTS** — โหลดไม่ได้\n4. **Kokoro** — ไม่มีเสียงไทย\n5. **gTTS** — เสียงหญิง\n\nไม่มี 5 ตัวที่ดีพอจะเอามาใช้ได้ครับ 😅\n\n**ทางเลือกที่เหลือ:**\n- ใช้ **Microsoft NiwatNeural** ที่มีอยู่ — เป็นผู้ชาย แต่ใน Linux อาจไม่ natural เท่าบน Windows\n- จ่ายตัวใช้ **Google Cloud TTS** หรือ **Elevenlabs**\n- รอมีคน train Thai male VITS แล้วปล่อยฟรี\n\nจะลอง Microsoft NiwatNeural ก่อนไหมครับ? 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":950,"output":733,"cacheRead":119040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120723,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778402101497,"responseId":"064f76368315e52fe965a8f6a3141ca0"}}
