{"type":"message","id":"91f9e2d8","parentId":"f9142b16","timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:42:21.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The boss doesn't want TTS to read out emojis at all. Every emoji should remain silent/not spoken.\n\nThis means we need to strip emojis from the text before sending to TTS. Let me think about how to do this...\n\nWe can strip emojis using a regex pattern or by detecting Unicode emoji ranges and removing them before TTS synthesis.\n","thinkingSignature":"0062ae4a510a31b457b68a60c39013e666f18c4e8941dc773abd59a4d7f1d194"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nเข้าใจครับ — ต้องลบ emojis ออกก่อนส่ง TTS\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dn9ql738gocs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport re\n\ndef remove_emojis(text):\n    # Remove all emojis (Unicode ranges)\n    emoji_pattern = re.compile(\n        '['\n        '\\U0001F600-\\U0001F64F'  # emoticons\n        '\\U0001F300-\\U0001F5FF'  # symbols & pictographs\n        '\\U0001F680-\\U0001F6FF'  # transport & map symbols\n        '\\U0001F700-\\U0001F77F'  # alchemical symbols\n        '\\U0001F780-\\U0001F7FF'  # Geometric Shapes Extended\n        '\\U0001F800-\\U0001F8FF'  # Supplemental Arrows-C\n        '\\U0001F900-\\U0001F9FF'  # Supplemental Symbols and Pictographs\n        '\\U0001FA00-\\U0001FA6F'  # Chess Symbols\n        '\\U0001FA70-\\U0001FAFF'  # Symbols and Pictographs Extended-A\n        '\\U00002702-\\U000027B0'  # Dingbats\n        '\\U000024C2-\\U0001F251'  # enclosed characters\n        '\\U0001F191-\\U0001F19A'  # Squared Latin Capital Letters\n        '\\U0001F200-\\U0001F202'  # Squared CJK Unified Ideographs\n        '\\U0001F232-\\U0001F23A'  # Squared CJK Unified Ideographs\n        '\\U0001F250-\\U0001F251'  # Circled Ideographs\n        '\\U00002600-\\U000026FF'  # Misc symbols\n        '\\U00002700-\\U000027BF'  # Dingbats\n        '\\U0001F900-\\U0001F92F'  # Supplemental Symbols and Pictographs\n        '\\U0001F000-\\U0001F02F'  # Mahjong Tiles\n        '\\U0001F0A0-\\U0001F0FF'  # Playing Cards\n        ']+', flags=re.UNICODE)\n    return emoji_pattern.sub(r'', text)\n\ntest = 'สวัสดีครับ 👋 ผมโอเว่น 🚀 เบอร์โทร 081-234-5678 ✅'\nprint('Before:', test)\nprint('After:', remove_emojis(test))\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":665,"output":664,"cacheRead":121280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":122609,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778402505843,"responseId":"064f77cca7394419a01c8de8736cee9e"}}
